pl.marcinmazur.portfolio.controller

Class AdminController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.marcinmazur.portfolio.controller.AdminController

  • @Controller
 @RequestMapping(value="/administrator-panel")
public class AdminController
extends Object
    The controller class is used to return the view depending on the user request. This controller contains the views of:
    • "dashboard"
    • "parts/statistic-table"
    • "contact-form-messages"
    • "parts/contact-form-message-table"
    • "parts/message-modal"
    • "access-codes"
    • "statistics"
    • "tasks"
    Author:
    Marcin Mazur
